# ToolBite — Cursor Permanent Rules

## Dark Mode (MANDATORY)
Every Tailwind class that sets color MUST include both light and dark variants.
Never write a color class without its dark counterpart.

### Backgrounds
- bg-white → bg-white dark:bg-gray-800
- bg-gray-50 → bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700
- bg-gray-100 → bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700
- bg-indigo-50 → bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/30
- bg-blue-50 → bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30
- bg-green-50 → bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30
- bg-red-50 → bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/30

### Text
- text-gray-900 → text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100
- text-gray-800 → text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200
- text-gray-700 → text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300
- text-gray-600 → text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400
- text-gray-500 → text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400

### Borders
- border-gray-100 → border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700
- border-gray-200 → border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600
- border-gray-300 → border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600

### Shadows
- shadow-xl → shadow-xl dark:shadow-gray-900/50
- shadow-md → shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/40
- shadow-sm → shadow-sm dark:shadow-gray-900/30

## Component Standards (MANDATORY)
- Cards: always use .tb-card or .tb-card--hover from global.css
- Buttons: always use .tb-btn + .tb-btn--primary / --secondary / --ghost
- NO inline Tailwind for new cards or buttons

## Meta Descriptions (MANDATORY)
- Every new HTML page must have a unique meta description
- Length: exactly 150-160 characters
- Must describe the specific page content, no generic phrases

## SEO (MANDATORY)
- Every new page needs: title, meta description, canonical link
- Heading hierarchy: one H1 per page, then H2, H3 in order
- All images: alt, width, height, loading="lazy"

## JavaScript (MANDATORY)
- No console.log statements in production code
- Theme toggle must use data-theme="dark"/"light" on <html> element
- No localStorage or sessionStorage usage

## Git (MANDATORY)
- Never commit: .DS_Store, seo-meta-descriptions.csv, *.log
- Commit messages format: type: short description
  Types: feat / fix / seo / style / refactor / docs
